{"blogid": "124076668", "writerAge": "码龄5年", "writerBlogNum": "16", "writerCollect": "221", "writerComment": "45", "writerFan": "36", "writerGrade": "3级", "writerIntegral": "621", "writerName": "百学成瘾", "writerProfileAdress": "writer_image\\profile_124076668.jpg", "writerRankTotal": "56216", "writerRankWeekly": "489537", "writerThumb": "93", "writerVisitNum": "55784", "blog_read_count": "1694", "blog_time": "已于 2022-04-10 14:35:54 修改", "blog_title": "VS2017获取工具和功能找不到visual stdio安装程序解决办法", "content": "<div class=\"article_content clearfix\" id=\"article_content\">\n<link href=\"style.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n<div class=\"markdown_views prism-atom-one-light\" id=\"content_views\">\n<svg style=\"display: none;\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n<path d=\"M5,0 0,2.5 5,5z\" id=\"raphael-marker-block\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"></path>\n</svg>\n<h4><a id=\"_0\"></a>我的问题</h4>\n<blockquote>\n<p>之前安装了vs2017，但是仅仅用来写C++程序<br/> 现在想用C#做窗体应用，需要安装C#模块<br/> 于是按照步骤 点击 <strong>工具-&gt;获取工具和功能</strong> 却出现如下现象<br/> <mark>找不到visual stdio 安装程序</mark></p>\n</blockquote>\n<center>\n<img src=\"image\\bdc90186bd814ce08ea2e6aa5a9aec35.png\" width=\"40%\"/>\n</center>\n<p>搜索了很久,按照知乎<a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/94927424\">安装installer组件</a>没有成功后，另辟蹊径</p>\n<ol><li><strong>前往C:\\Program Files (x86)\\Microsoft Visual Studio\\Installer</strong>(自己vs的安装路径)</li><li><strong>右键点击【vs_installershell.exe】-【以管理员运行】</strong></li></ol>\n<p>直接打开installer安装C#组件，<mark>大功告成</mark>！</p>\n<h3><a id=\"_17\"></a><strong>下面是安装过程的一些图示：</strong></h3>\n<p>打开vs_installershell.exe后显示如下，点击修改</p>\n<center>\n<img src=\"image\\58c33fc4a3bd40148ff1e95bc3e4e2c6.png\" width=\"80%\"/>\n</center>\n<p>按照我的需求添加如下两个C#相关组件后，确定修改</p>\n<center>\n<img src=\"image\\634418af5d75417b832522752c88c145.png\" width=\"80%\"/>\n</center>\n<p>根据相应提示，点击继续，会自动下载安装，安装成功后，打开VS</p>\n<center>\n<img src=\"image\\7efb2632dd714ad2b4ce3ab7a0204b7c.png\" width=\"80%\"/>\n</center>\n<p>可以看到，已安装下面出现了**visual C#**组件</p>\n<center>\n<img src=\"image\\79e4bad188e846bd8c61c04ad1120587.png\" width=\"80%\"/>\n</center>\n<p>创建窗体应用后如下</p>\n<center>\n<img src=\"image\\b04144c3f487427b86c7e9414d7689a1.png\" width=\"80%\"/>\n</center>\n<p>End！</p>\n</div>\n<link href=\"https://csdnimg.cn/release/blogv2/dist/mdeditor/css/editerView/markdown_views-22a2fefd3b.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n<link href=\"https://csdnimg.cn/release/blogv2/dist/mdeditor/css/style-4f8fbf9108.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n</div>"}